Sleep 300ms
Hide
Type `printf '\e[H\e[J\n\e[1;33m━━ Summary ━━\e[0m\n\n\e[38;5;245m  • Kubernaut detected KubeStatefulSetReplicasMismatch alert from Prometheus\n  • AI analysis identified: broken PVC with wrong StorageClass\n  • Selected workflow: RecreatePVC (auto-approved)\n  • Workflow recreated PVC\n  • Users notified via Slack and console\n  • EffectivenessAssessment confirmed: remediation successful\e[0m\n'`
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Show
Sleep 15s
